"first 7 edges, then 2, then JUMPS to 10 on single bridge edge." . cr
"Substrate-readable PERCOLATION PHASE TRANSITION verified." . cr
cr
"Canonical star order: observer's component size grows linearly" . cr
"1 → 2 → 3 → ... → 10.  No discontinuity.  Same substrate, same" . cr
"primitives — but DIFFERENT order parameter trajectory based on" . cr
"edge-addition history." . cr
cr
"FIRST substrate-readable measure in the catalogue exhibiting" . cr
"genuine phase-transition behaviour.  Φ_PA family (degree-based)" . cr
"does not; component-size (graph-theoretic) does." . cr
cr
